items.title: Deepak Nitrite announces Rs 3,500 crore major capex to boost supply chain as demand for speciality chemicals swells
items.description: Deepak Nitrite's subsidiary has approved a major investment to set up a new manufacturing complex, in an effort to expanding domestic production of key speciality chemicals, a move that is seen as a step to further de-risk the supply chain in present times for trade-related disruptions.

items.description: Prada has negotiated for months to buy the fashion house founded by Gianni Versace in the 1970s and known for its flashy, ready-to-wear designs.
